works.complaint:
I am contacting you due to the search results which  
appear after my name is typed into google. After, the end of a violent  
marriage my ex-husband had been posting pictures/videos of me onto
websites  
etc. Although, these (most of them) had been removed, my name still comes 

up with these defamatory search results. I have been informing my local  
police of the on-going issues and they have said to try and contact you  
with regards to having this removed. I cannot express enough how much of a
 
negative effect this is having on my personal and professional life.
Please  
can you do something to ensure my name does not come up with such results.
 
Please get back to me as soon as possible, as i am finding this very  
distressing. Many Thanks. Ateayah Ashraf
